title: Think Google Calendar Is Just For Meetings? You're Missing Out
description: How to use the app as a productivity tool, plus more (free) tricks to make you more efficient at work

title: Former Outcome Health Executives Found Guilty of Fraud
description: A federal jury convicted the former CEO and two other ex-executives of the once-highflying startup on charges that they defrauded customers and investors.

title: Judge Rejects Theranos Founder Holmes's Bid to Stay Out of Prison
description: The judge said in a filing that he didn’t think Elizabeth Holmes’s arguments for reversing her conviction or getting a new trial raised issues significant enough to merit a different outcome.

title: China Lays Out Rules for ChatGPT-Like Tools
description: The proposed rules would give Beijing power over services using the technology as Alibaba and Huawei join rush to offer services.

title: AI-Created Images Are So Good Even AI Has Trouble Spotting Some
description: Software tools can help you determine the origin of an image, but context is still key.

title: South Korea Fines Google $32 Million for Squeezing Out Local Rival
description: Google’s tactics of blocking the growth of rival app marketplace One Store amounted to anticompetitive practices, South Korea’s Fair Trade Commission says.

title: Biden Administration Weighs Possible Rules for AI Tools Like ChatGPT
description: Fears are growing over the potential use of artificial intelligence to commit crimes and spread falsehoods.
